title: Consumptive Field
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

During the Psychic Phase, the [[Doom of Malan'tai]] may consume warp charges to recover wounds lost earlier in the battle, regaining a single wound per warp charge devoured if it passes a Leadership test.